<A>__{aerial angle. in the sun's last light, two figures walk slowly, far below us. the vega waits. close angle. they stand beneath the wing. her ground crew in far distance, giving them their moment. her look is not breezy and cavalier this time, but tender and intimate. she knows the fear beneath his easy smile. he produces a ring, a band of black fibers.}
